    <h2 class="cag-h2">How Two Families Chose</h2>
    <p>We could summarize a decade of these decisions, but two of our verified buyers say it better than we can. Both weighed the same Congo-vs-Timneh question you're weighing, and their stories sit alongside dozens more on our <a href="/african-grey-reviews/">African Grey reviews</a> page — here's what actually mattered to each.</p>
